nodes.text: During the Cold War, a male Twi'lek lived on the world of Tython as a member of the Twi'lek Pilgrims that chose to colonize this world. At some point during the final year of the war, this Twi'lek wanted to prove himself to Nalen Raloch when he entered the Fount of Rajivari, but was badly wounded from the traps he faced.
